{"tid":2291744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★勞福局將透過跨部門計劃助年輕人赴大灣區就業 月薪由一萬五千元至二萬元","createTime":"2020-11-19T04:07:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-21T05:25:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"f92e64457d30906e316d2311a5f622652fa586bb","tid":2291744,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:07:30.000Z","msg":"消息指，勞工及福利局將牽頭透過跨部門計劃協助年輕人到大灣區就業。<br />\n<br />\n新一份《施政報告》將於下周三公布。消息指，政府將會與大灣區內科技、金融等企業，包括騰訊進行配對計劃，為香港年輕人提供數千個職位，並由港府提供資助。<br />\n<br />\n參與計劃的年輕人<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>月薪由一萬五千元至二萬元</strong></span>不等，相關計劃細節仍在敲定中，初步為期一年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5fb5e6bc34b0315155cec380/%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%8B%9E%E7%A6%8F%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%87%E7%89%BD%E9%A0%AD%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E8%B7%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%8A%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5fb5e6bc34b0315155cec380%2F%25E6%2593%259A%25E6%2582%2589%25E5%258B%259E%25E7%25A6%258F%25E5%25B1%2580%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2589%25BD%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%2580%258F%25E9%2581%258E%25E8%25B7%25A8%25E9%2583%25A8%25E9%2596%2580%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583%25E5%258A%25A9%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25BC%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%2581%25A3%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD&d=VbAd486K8RrC2DEUtq3b5jBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=a271a7b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5fb5e6bc34b0315155cec380/%E6%93%9A%E6%82%89%E5%8B%9E%E7%A6%8F%E5%B1%80%E5%B0%87%E7%89%BD%E9%A0%AD%E9%80%8F%E9%81%8E%E8%B7%A8%E9%83%A8%E9%96%80%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83%E5%8A%A9%E5%B9%B4%E8%BC%95%E4%BA%BA%E8%B5%B4%E5%A4%A7%E7%81%A3%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD</a>"},{"pid":"f1e92f6556971494da1e324dda74f5340153feeb","tid":2291744,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-19T04:07:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj